{"tid":2365344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"創立Signal來打返自己創立的WhatsApp ！！！","createTime":"2021-01-13T15:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T17:14:59.000Z","uid":96443,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f3bd4a8dc3e1ccdebe6ecb7f903484dfce509ba9","tid":2365344,"uid":96443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><br />\n<br />\n可能好多人知, 不過我唔知. 原來近來爆紅嘅Signal的其中一個創辦人Mr. Brian Acton, 亦都係WhatsApp的其中一個創辦人. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp係2014年被Facebook收購左之後, Brian Acton因為不同意Facebook在客戶資料/廣告推廣方面不太尊重用戶私隱度的政策而離開咗WhatsApp. 如果Brian 選擇遲一年先離開Facebook, 佢將會多收8.5億美金的Facebook股票. (不過可能佢唔care, 因為賣WhatsApp單deal佢賺咗30億美金. 點都好佢有骨氣, 道不同不相為謀). <br />\n<br />\n係一個訪問當中Brian表達咗佢覺得對唔住Whatsapp的用戶. 皆因佢自己係好唔鍾意廣告, 佢創立WhatsApp, 就係想比用戶係一個冇廣告滋擾下的環境來溝通. 但係最後佢竟然把WhatsApp賣咗比全世界最大用廣告來賺錢的公司Facebook. 跟據Brian所講, 佢嘗試過游說Facebook高層把WhatsApp改變為一個收錢的App. 舉例, 如果send超過某個數目的訊息就會開始收錢. 不過Facebook的高層聽到就已經唔係太中意. 所以佢嬲嬲地之下就辭職走人. 其實10幾年之前Brian喺Yahoo!打工的時候亦都係因為唔同意Yahoo!係所有版面都放廣告banner而辭職. (所以大家如果有機會同佢做嘢就千祈唔好睇提廣告兩個字, 如果唔係佢會辭職). <br />\n<br />\n之後在2018年Brian Acton投放了5,000萬美金,自己錢,創辦了一個非牟利組織: Signal Foundation, 即係Signal App 的創辦組織. 佢希望重拾WhatsApp的初衷以免費, 冇廣告, 最尊重客戶私隱的方式來提供一個Messenger比大家. Signal Foundation長遠的營運經費將會以自願募捐形式來籌集. <br />\n<br />\nBrian講過一句, Facebook果班唔係衰人, 佢哋只係好叻的生意人. <br />\n<br />\n適逢巨變, Rolodex都會繼續在Telegram的Channel 發文: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/RfVkjPXzcIsz1VGN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FRfVkjPXzcIsz1VGN&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=b8e4991c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/RfVkjPXzcIsz1VGN</a><br />\n希望得到大家支持. <br />\n<br />\n資料來源: <br />\nForbes Magazine<br />\nSignal 官方網站</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xKMyN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xKMyN9.jpg&h=dd90a919&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1938bced863df1efc4b1b84e764feb78d6562006","tid":2365344,"uid":96443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b798f2a2749d1d483afff5f8dfd979c9e4a06f6","tid":2365344,"uid":96443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2f37f8e87f60d4471e304eac5f936312531c3539","tid":2365344,"uid":28485,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"支持下佢地<br />\n如果唔係啲問題好難改善"},{"pid":"68803e3e40eb229e06c813671d8c4601d267d78b","tid":2365344,"uid":352074,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"佢已經賣咗啦<br />\n到時將signal做大左之後再買俾其他人又可以賺一大筆<br />\nFatfat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9474b3b2f7e1d7958c17380fffd5bf580be11d3","tid":2365344,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"支持高質頻道"},{"pid":"47a3380da8c68203be0849f0538809749a6a3ba6","tid":2365344,"uid":165659,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"68803e3e40eb229e06c813671d8c4601d267d78b","tid":2365344,"uid":352074,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"佢已經賣咗啦<br />\n到時將signal做大左之後再買俾其他人又可以賺一大筆<br />\nFatfat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"ngo都有得賣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁宣明會奥比斯幾時上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097428f35c73efa406313b68e747d89584bd4b7a","tid":2365344,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"